
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <!-- Favicon icon -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="./images/favicon.png">
    <link href="./css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">

</head>

<body>
    <div class="content-body">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row page-titles mx-0">
                <!-- row -->
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-12">
                        <div class="profile">
                            <div class="profile-head">
                                <div class="profile-info">
                                    <div class="row justify-content-center">
                                        <div class="col-xl-8">
                                            <div class="row">
                                                @if (User.Identity.IsAuthenticated)
                                                {
                                                string id = User.Claims.FirstOrDefault(c => c.Type == System.Security.Claims.ClaimTypes.NameIdentifier)?.Value;
                                                string filePath = "~/imgPessoa/" + id + ".jpg";
                                                Url.Content(filePath);
                                                <div class="photo-content">

                                                    <div class="profile-photo">
                                                        <img src="@Url.Content(filePath)" class="img-fluid rounded-circle" alt="this is your profile image">
                                                    </div>
                                                    
                                                    <br />
                                                </div>
                                                }
                                                <div style="align-content: start;" class="col-xl-10 col-sm-4 border-right-1 prf-col">
                                                    <div class="profile-name">
                                                        <h4 class="text-primary">Pedro da Silva</h4>
                                                        <p>Desenvolvedor De Software</p>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="profile-statistics">
                                    <div class="text-center mt-4 border-bottom-1 pb-3">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col">
                                                <h3 class="m-b-0">150</h3><span>Seguidores</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col">
                                                <h3 class="m-b-0">100</h3><span>Seguindo</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col">
                                                <h3 class="m-b-0">45</h3><span>Visitas ao Perfil</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="mt-4">
                                            <a href="javascript:void()" class="btn btn-primary pl-5 pr-5 mr-3 mb-4">Seguir</a>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="profile-blog pt-3 border-bottom-1 pb-1">
                                    <h5 class="text-primary d-inline">Você pode gostar também:</h5><a href="javascript:void()" class="pull-right f-s-16"></a>
                                    <img src="~/img/profile/entra21-profile-image.png" alt="" class="img-fluid mt-4 mb-4 w-100">
                                    <h4>Amostra de Talentos Entra21</h4>
                                    <p>Durante os dias 20/10 e 21/10 acontecerá a amostra de talentos do curso Entra21. Diversos alunos de Blumenau irão mostrar seus projetos onde compareceram também as empresas parceiras do curso.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="profile-interest mt-4 pb-2 border-bottom-1">
                                    <h5 class="text-primary d-inline">Interesses</h5>
                                    <div class="row mt-4">
                                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-xl-4 col-sm-4 col-6 int-col">
                                            <a href="javascript:void()" class="interest-cat">
                                                <p>Festas</p>
                                            </a>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-xl-4 col-sm-4 col-6 int-col">
                                            <a href="javascript:void()" class="interest-cat">
                                                <p>Eventos Gerais</p>
                                            </a>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-xl-4 col-sm-4 col-6 int-col">
                                            <a href="javascript:void()" class="interest-cat">
                                                <p>Palestras</p>
                                            </a>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-8">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="profile-tab">
                                    <div class="custom-tab-1">
                                        <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
                                            <li class="nav-item">
                                                <a href="#my-posts" data-toggle="tab" class="nav-link active show">Posts</a>
                                            </li>
                                            <li class="nav-item">
                                                <a href="#about-me" data-toggle="tab" class="nav-link">Sobre mim</a>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <div class="tab-content">
                                            <div id="my-posts" class="tab-pane fade active show">
                                                <div class="my-post-content pt-3">
                                                    <div class="post-input">
                                                        <textarea name="textarea" id="textarea" cols="30" rows="5" class="form-control bg-transparent" placeholder="Escreva oque você está pensando..."></textarea> <a href="javascript:void()"><i class="ti-clip"></i> </a>
                                                        <br />
                                                        <a href="javascript:void()"><i class="ti-camera"></i> </a><a href="javascript:void()" class="btn btn-primary">Postar</a>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <hr />
                                                    <br />
                                                    <div class="profile-uoloaded-post border-bottom-1 pb-5">
                                                        <img style="width: 908px; height: 359px;" src="/img/profile/profile-party-image.png" alt="" class="img-fluid">
                                                        <br />
                                                        <br />
                                                        <div>

                                                        </div>
                                                        <a class="post-title" href="javascript:void()">
                                                            <h4 href="">Festa De Encerramento de Curso</h4>
                                                        </a>
                                                        <p>
                                                            Festa de Encerramento de curso na Proway Centro de Blumenau. Dia 23/10/21
                                                        </p>
                                                        <button style="margin: 2px;" class="btn btn-primary mr-3">
                                                            <span class="mr-3">
                                                                <i class="fa fa-thumbs-up"></i>
                                                            </span>Like
                                                        </button>
                                                        <button style="margin: 2px;" class="btn btn-primary mr-3">
                                                            <span>
                                                                <i class="fa fa-thumbs-down"></i>
                                                            </span>Dislike
                                                        </button>

                                                        <button class="btn btn-secondary">
                                                            <span class="mr-3">
                                                                <i class="fa fa-reply"></i>
                                                            </span>Compartilhar
                                                        </button>
                                                        <button style="margin: 2px;" class="btn btn-secondary">
                                                            <i> vtmnc</i>
                                                        </button>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="about-me" class="tab-pane fade">
                                                <div class="profile-about-me">
                                                    <div class="pt-4 border-bottom-1 pb-4">
                                                        <h4 class="text-primary">Sobre Mim</h4>
                                                        <p>
                                                            Olá me chamo Pedro tenho 20 anos, atualmente trabalho como desenvolvedor de software e no meu tempo livre gosto muito de festas e estou em busca de novas companhias e amizades para ir as festas comigo. Se gostar do meu perfil e gostos me siga :)
                                                        </p>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="profile-skills pt-2 border-bottom-1 pb-2">
                                                    <h4 class="text-primary mb-4">Gostos Pessoais</h4>
                                                    <a href="javascript:void()" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-rounded pl-4 my-3 my-sm-0 pr-4 mr-3 m-b-10">Narguile</a>
                                                    <a href="javascript:void()" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-rounded pl-4 my-3 my-sm-0 pr-4 mr-3 m-b-10">Bebidas</a>
                                                    <a href="javascript:void()" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-rounded pl-4 my-3 my-sm-0 pr-4 mr-3 m-b-10">Funk</a>
                                                    <a href="javascript:void()" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-rounded pl-4 my-3 my-sm-0 pr-4 mr-3 m-b-10">Novas Amizades</a>
                                                </div>
                                                <br />
                                                <div class="profile-personal-info">
                                                    <h4 class="text-primary mb-4">Informações Pessoais</h4>
                                                    <div class="row mb-4">
                                                        <div class="col-3">
                                                            <h5 class="f-w-500">
                                                                Nome <span class="pull-right">:</span>
                                                            </h5>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="col-9">
                                                            <span>Pedro da Silva</span>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="row mb-4">
                                                        <div class="col-3">
                                                            <h5 class="f-w-500">
                                                                Idade <span class="pull-right">:</span>
                                                            </h5>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="col-9">
                                                            <span>20</span>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="row mb-4">
                                                        <div class="col-3">
                                                            <h5 class="f-w-500">Cidade<span class="pull-right">:</span></h5>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="col-9">
                                                            <span>
                                                                Blumenau-SC
                                                            </span>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>

                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    <!-- Required vendors -->
    <script src="~/js/demo/uploadImages.js"></script>
    <script src="./vendor/global/global.min.js"></script>
    <script src="./js/quixnav-init.js"></script>
    <script src="./js/custom.min.js"></script>


    

</body>

</html>